Queries

autoCollects

Response

Returns a PaginatedCollectionResponse!

Arguments
Name Description
input - UserCollectionsInput!

Example

Query
query AutoCollects($input: UserCollectionsInput!) {
  autoCollects(input: $input) {
    items {
      id
      name
      image
      userId
      shareLink
      user {
        ...PartialUserBaseFragment
      }
      preview {
        ...CollectionItemFragment
      }
      users {
        ...CollectionUserFragment
      }
      recipient {
        ...CollectionUserFragment
      }
      autoCollectApprovals {
        ...AutoCollectApprovalFragment
      }
      shared
      itemCount
      attachments {
        ...UploadFragment
      }
      permissionsMetadata {
        ...PermissionsMetadataFragment
      }
    }
    pager {
      totalItems
      currentPage
      pageSize
      totalPages
      startPage
      endPage
      startIndex
      endIndex
      pages
    }
  }
}
Variables
{"input": UserCollectionsInput}
Response
{
  "data": {
    "autoCollects": {
      "items": [Collection],
      "pager": Pager
    }
  }
}

Field Name Description

friend - FriendStatus!
